<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Enregistrés | SocialVibe</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css">
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-dark-100 text-gray-900 dark:text-white min-h-screen">
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
        <%- include('partials/sidebar') %>

            <main class="lg:ml-64 pt-16">
                <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-6">
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Éléments enregistrés</h1>
                    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-dark-200 rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 text-center">
                        <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto text-gray-300 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                d="M5 5a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v16l-7-3.5L5 21V5z" />
                        </svg>
                        <p class="text-gray-500">Vous n'avez aucun élément enregistré pour le moment.</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-2">Enregistrez des posts pour les retrouver ici plus tard.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
            <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>

</html>